  "privacyLastUpdated": "শেষ আপডেট: মার্চ ২০২৫",
  "privacyIntro": "At {appName}, your গোপনীয়তা is paramount. This গোপনীয়তা Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal and health-related data. By using our services, you agree to the practices described below.",
  "privacySectionDataCollection": "১. তথ্য সংগ্রহ",
  "privacyDataCollectionBody": "We collect the following categories of data: • Personal Information: Nনাম ইমেইল address, ফোন number, তারিখ of birth, and gender. • স্বাস্থ্য Data: Blood type, aঅ্যালার্জি chronic conditions, mওষুধ vital signs, symptom logs, and ট্রায়েজ results. • জরুরি Contacts: Names, ফোন numbers, and relationships of your designated contacts. • Device Data: Device type, operating system, and app version for compatibility and sসহায়তা • Usage Data: Feature interactions and anonymized analytics to improve our services. We only collect data that is necessary for providing our স্বাস্থ্য companion services. You have full control over what information you provide.",
  "privacySectionDataStorage": "২. ডেটা সংরক্ষণ ও এনক্রিপশন",
  "privacyDataStorageBody": "Your data is stored using industry-leading security measures:\n\n• Encryption at Rest: All data stored in our databases is encrypted using AES-256 encryption.\n• Encryption in Transit: All data transmitted between your device and our servers uses TLS 1.3 encryption.\n• Health Passport: Your health passport data is encrypted with a unique key derived from your credentials.\n• QR কোড Sharing: Shared health data via QR codes is encrypted and time-limited.\n• Infrastructure: Our servers are hosted in SOC 2 Type II certified data centers with 24/7 monitoring.\n\nWe do not store payment card information. All payment processing is handled by certified third-party providers.",
  "privacySectionGdpr": "৩. জিডিপিআর সম্মতি",
  "privacyGdprBody": "{appName} is fully compliant with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR): • Lawful Basis: We process your data based on your explicit consent and contractual necessity. • Data Minimization: We only collect and process data that is strictly necessary. • Purpose Limitation: Your data is used only for the purposes for which it was collected. • Right to Access: You can request a complete copy of your personal data at any tসময় • Right to Rectification: You can update or correct your data through the app sসেটিংস • Right to Erasure: You can request complete deletion of your account and data. • Right to Portability: You can রপ্তানি your data in a machine-readable format. • Data Processing Agreements: সব third-party processors have signed DPAs. • Cross-Border Transfers: Data is processed within the EU/EEA unless explicit consent is given otherwise.",
  "privacySectionYourRights": "৪. আপনার অধিকার",
  "privacyRightsBody": "You have the following rights regarding your data: • Access: View সব your personal and স্বাস্থ্য data within the app or request a data eরপ্তানি • Correction: সম্পাদনা your প্রোফাইল information at any সময় through সম্পাদনা Pপ্রোফাইল • Deletion: Request account deletion through সেটিংস > Data & গোপনীয়তা > মুছুন Account. • Restriction: Limit how certain data is processed by adjusting your notification and sharing preferences. • Objection: Object to specific data processing activities by contacting our Data Protection Officer. • Withdrawal of Consent: You may withdraw consent at any সময় without affecting the lawfulness of prior processing. To exercise any of these rights, contact us at privacy@vitalseker.com or through the in-app সহায়তা feature.",
  "privacySectionContactUs": "৫. আমাদের সাথে যোগাযোগ করুন",
  "privacyContactBody": "If you have any questions or concerns সম্পর্কে this গোপনীয়তা Policy or our data practices, please contact us: • Eইমেইল privacy@vitalseker.com • Sসহায়তা support@vitalseker.com • Data Protection Officer: dpo@vitalseker.com • Address: {producer}, Data Protection Office We aim to respond to সব privacy-related inquiries within 30 days.",
